ltatene ble presentert under \u00e5rets forum for europeisk nevrovitenskap i Wien i \u00d8sterrike. Braun forsker for tiden, sammen med psykiatere, p\u00e5 om virkningene av stress i svangerskapet kan reverseres etter f\u00f8dselen."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|helse"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "29c262a5581e8616a67e55196bd26f894edff0f7a28b05bf31550fb1e99f536c"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2013-05-22T17:33:12.774Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Stress under svangerskapet kan f\u00e5 alvorlige konsekvenser for barnet."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1171465.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Gravid"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/0102a8efac5e5ae844232d9796b07063e240a9c0.jpg?588427dd"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Gravide m\u00e5 unng\u00e5 stress -adressa.no", "Alvorlige konsekvenser", "Ulik effekt"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "0102a8efac5e5ae844232d9796b07063e240a9c0"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "helse"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["stress", "unng\u00e5 stress"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["teknisk ukeblad", "new scientist"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["wien", "jerusalem", "magdeburg", "\u00f8sterrike", "tyskland", "israel"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "katharina braun"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/helse"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1171465.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Gravid"},